SUMMARY:Hiefoda Tunes
LOCATION:Not Nothing
DESCRIPTION:Treating record-spinning like mad science\n\nA four-headed beas
 t wired on bad ideas and good instincts\, turning chaos into something tha
 t somehow grooves.\nHiefoda Tunes sets spiral\, stutter and snap into plac
 e with a cheeky sense of humor. Five years deep as Best Kept Secret legend
 s\, they keep coming back like a glitch that won’t fix itself. Breakbeat
 s breaking\, cold cuts freezing\, deep grooves diggin deeper...you know th
 e deal!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-18d352da813d9520@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T190000Z
DTEND:20260613T210000Z
SUMMARY:Night Dubbing
LOCATION:Not Nothing
DESCRIPTION:Steely jungle and DnB from the early days\n\nTheir partnership 
 started under a bridge in Amersfoort\, and continues at Best Kept Secret.M
 eet Night Dubbing\, the mystery junglist massive out of Amersfoort. Locals
  in the game\, you might have caught them at the after hours in the red cu
 be or at your favorite festival. As Night Dubbing this couple will share t
 heir unusual selection of steely jungle and DnB from the early days.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-d5fa7b06a5cb124d@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T210000Z
DTEND:20260613T223000Z
SUMMARY:Tim Reaper
LOCATION:Not Nothing
DESCRIPTION:Jungle revivalist & revisionist\n\nWithin the recent jungle gol
 drush\, Tim Reaper has played a major part in shaping its modern day ident
 ity.\nA stamp marked by his own aerodynamic take on jungle and as founder 
 of Future Retro\, which platforms emerging DJ talent from contemporary jun
 gle and drum&bass scenes around the world. Through collaboration\, Reaper 
 blends the foundational influence of jungle with club movements like techn
 o and footwork\, creating the best kind of chaos possible.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
